    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhap3isd2/image/upload/v1718628554/Kriapay_wordmark_logo_1_l0vi2m.png"
          alt="Kriapay Logo"
        />
        <h1>Password Reset Requested</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= user.firstName %>,</p>
        <p>
          We just wanted to let you know that you have requested to change your Kriapay password. If you requested for this change, you can continue below. If you did not request the change, please contact our support team immediately at
          <a href="mailto:support@kriapay.com">support@kriapay.com</a>.
        </p>
        <p>Kindly enter the following number to continue:</p>
      <p style="background:#F5F5F5;display:inline-block; font-weight:700; margin-top:24px; color:#000;text-transform:uppercase; font-size:20px;padding:10px 30px;display:inline-block;letter-spacing:25px;"><%= otp %></p>

        <p>For your security, remember to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Use a strong and unique password/pin.</li>
          <li>Avoid sharing your password/pin with anyone.</li>
          <li>Regularly update your password to enhance security.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Thank you for being a valued member of the Kriapay community!</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Kriapay Team</p>
